      * Modulo de acceso a nueva Subrutina de Garantias GARPGRCC en vez de
      * antigua GARPGRGA
       IDG-PUT-RGA SECTION.
       INI-IDG-PUT-RGA.
      *DAD ini  12-JUN-1991 
      *     CALL 'GARPGRGA' USING RGA-LINK.

           EXEC CICS HANDLE CONDITION
                     PGMIDERR (ERR-IDG-PUT-RGA)
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE 'GARPGRCC' TO SYS-PROG.
           MOVE RGA-TCMA   TO SYS-TCMA.
      *     MOVE RGA-LINK   TO SYS-CMMA.
      *     MOVE SYS-LINK   TO SYS-CMND.
      *     PERFORM GNS-PRO-SYS.
      *     MOVE SYS-CMMA   TO RGA-LINK.
           EXEC CICS LINK
                     PROGRAM (SYS-PROG)
                     COMMAREA(RGA-LINK)
                     LENGTH  (SYS-TCMA)
           END-EXEC.
      *DAD fin  12-JUN-1991 

           IF RGA-COD-STAT NOT > SPACES
               MOVE '00' TO FIO-STAT
           ELSE
               MOVE '13' TO FIO-STAT.

      *DAD ini  12-JUN-1991 
           GO TO FIN-IDG-PUT-RGA.
       ERR-IDG-PUT-RGA.
           MOVE 'NO EXISTE PROGRAMA : ' TO SYS-MEN1.
           MOVE SYS-PROG                TO SYS-MEN2.
           MOVE SYS-ABOR                TO SYS-CMND.
           PERFORM GNS-PRO-SYS.
      *DAD fin  12-JUN-1991 
       FIN-IDG-PUT-RGA.
           EXIT.
